20:13.696 --> 20:16.863
I can't believe it. Pushin'
books. And they're all Y.A.

20:16.865 --> 20:18.441
<i> The Fault in Our Stars.</i>

20:18.443 --> 20:20.943
Only one person dies
and they don't even get whacked.

20:20.945 --> 20:23.221
I did like<i> Divergent.</i>
Lot of people get whacked.

20:23.223 --> 20:26.449
This is gonna be one long
15-to-life.

20:26.451 --> 20:32.104
-Idiota!
-(both yelling in Italian)

21:21.672 --> 21:22.697
Shh!
